1 make a scoring matrix 
Scoring matrix is where matrix is made on the bases of match and mis-match
Match is +1 , Mis-match is -1 , gap is -2
put value in Column 1 and last row
from diagonal box , keep the highest value in the box.
mark your directions 

Rules
A gap is there in the beginning on the x-axis and y-axix
BOX besides ( whatever is value add gap value)
BOX bottom  ( whatever is value add gap value)
Diagonal Box ( see match/ mis-match)

2. tracebacking
see the highest value
from the highest value trace back towards 0

3. Alignment
look for the traceback arrows and the direction
vertical arrow , horizontal put gap
diagonal arrow put characters of the sequence
